<td class="column-2">Justified on the basis of Pledge2Propel’s legitimate interests of ensuring that it recruits the appropriate employees.</td>
</tr>
<tr class="row-10 even">
<td class="column-1">Administration of employee benefits</td>
<td class="column-2">Justified on the basis of Pledge2Propel’s legitimate interests of ensuring that our employees receive the applicable benefits.</td>
</tr>
